Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.96,0:00:11.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救…救命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.76,0:00:13.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.98,0:00:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里  在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.51,0:00:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有听到什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.41,0:00:22.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果落下去了  在这样的暴风雨救上来是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.39,0:00:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还只是个少年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.43,0:00:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要成佛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.12,0:00:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.95,0:00:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别丢下我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.34,0:00:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么简单的放弃我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.14,0:00:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能那么简单的就死心了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.00,0:00:54.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样死心的话  不就相当于自己认输了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:00:58.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要变得和爸爸说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.87,0:01:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:13.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是果然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.43,0:01:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离家出走是错误的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.01,0:02:56.02,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂流到了  天国!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:17.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.95,0:03:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  炸猪排
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:26.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就做美味的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.24,0:03:29.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天有暴风雨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会有很大的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.43,0:03:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  那么快就有了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.15,0:03:43.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.54,0:03:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得…确实被大浪吞噬了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:43.71,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.86,0:03:46.09,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你  振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:47.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:50.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你  振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:56.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能死  把水排出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:03:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这种时候最后的手段是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.33,0:04:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是再发生什么真的要下地狱了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.49,0:04:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什什什什什什…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.57,0:04:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是地狱  这是…天国…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.53,0:04:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.54,0:04:21.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.05,0:04:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有好好按照所学的人工呼吸了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:28.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（去天国）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.41,0:04:36.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像外面的人漂流到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.08,0:04:42.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想救他却给他致命一击是想怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪  明明按照婆婆所说的那样做的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好看的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.92,0:04:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是外人第一次漂流到这个岛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.24,0:04:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很少见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:04:58.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.93,0:05:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子和我们有点不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.65,0:05:03.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部也平平的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.81,0:05:07.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不同  想知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.02,0:05:11.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为呐  铃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:12.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:14.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:15.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.24,0:05:17.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:20.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:21.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.72,0:05:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重  好重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去工作！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  这个那个都偷懒不工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.57,0:05:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子是男孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子会变得很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:52.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.86,0:06:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  没关…不会没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀～对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.60,0:06:08.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不单救了我  连饭都准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫东方院行人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫行人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是铃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.88,0:06:16.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃不喝一周漂流到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.39,0:06:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么连你也在吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我还以为漂流到了相当远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好还是在日本里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实住在这里的都是日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.77,0:06:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这岛在哪里可不知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:37.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是因为  其实我们也是漂流到了这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.62,0:06:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.74,0:06:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是距现在130年前的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.02,0:06:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本开国后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们为了学习最新的技术和医学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.21,0:06:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驶向欧洲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆您贵庚？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:07:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是途中碰到大风暴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.24,0:07:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然就漂流到了这个岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆幸的是这个岛容易居住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取了和沉没的船一样的名字  叫蓝兰岛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样生活到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:15.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:16.96,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:18.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还有这样的岛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.51,0:07:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你身穿的装饰  日本也改变的相当的大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:28.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有离开岛的船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.49,0:07:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样怎么才能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.19,0:07:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在别想多余的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:36.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在铃家里慢慢的养伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:39.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后的事情以后考虑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用船到附近的岛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里也许会有联络船或飞机吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  刚才就在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:55.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子是炸猪排
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.29,0:07:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:08:00.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时让你睡一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.32,0:08:00.84,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上让你好好吃一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.95,0:08:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:08.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:12.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在很忙  没空和你玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:15.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把人说的好像很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.67,0:08:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不要住在铃家比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃家非常的破烂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:23.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屋顶破了会漏水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有虫子老鼠一堆堆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:28.23,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人  骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:29.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  铃睡相很差
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.49,0:08:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还会尿床
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:32.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.39,0:08:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种差劲的攻击  对我是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:44.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么走吧  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可以吗  那样放着不管
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.13,0:08:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种程度  绫音没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:49.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种程度…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.41,0:08:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意被干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:56.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉在后面  找寻敌人的破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.19,0:08:58.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中我的计谋了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.49,0:09:00.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回吃我一招
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:01.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:08.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.32,0:09:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然身体还麻痹着  还过得去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  解毒药
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:16.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多被打中几次就会习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.65,0:09:18.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不想习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫音她从小就和我针锋相对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事就来找麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.05,0:09:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜负倒还好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:28.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管我是否愿意这一点  还真为难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.74,0:09:32.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说…说起来  你的家人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:33.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好晚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:36.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家双亲都没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:39.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  问了不该问的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.24,0:09:40.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:42.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是很久以前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.36,0:09:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是还真为难
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和女孩一起  两人同住一个屋檐下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.08,0:09:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  不行  不能想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  水温怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  完全没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那么我也进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…铃…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  帮你搓背吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…我已经洗过了  不…不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  别客气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.77,0:10:24.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢大家相互搓背了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互搓背？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:28.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:32.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常女生能无所谓的和男生一起进浴室吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  行人  舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也许就是岛上的风俗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:40.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回轮到行人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.98,0:10:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样我也平静的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…做不到！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:10:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  绫音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:10:59.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是从哪里冒出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.06,0:11:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想来擦洗行人大人的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:05.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到每一寸肌肤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.63,0:11:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那由我来做就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.05,0:11:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上  像你这样的小鬼  真的能让男士满足吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说小鬼还真失礼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:17.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫音你也不是又矮又平的  像小孩一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不得不和你做一回了断呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.08,0:11:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  热得晕过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  冷水拿过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.01,0:11:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.90,0:11:40.29,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜错了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:39.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.79,0:11:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  已经醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来带你参观这个岛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.11,0:11:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事无所谓  快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:55.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要～～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.54,0:12:07.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  公子  还真危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.07,0:12:12.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  绫音那家伙竟然偷跑  还真不能大意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:13.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.11,0:12:17.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是木匠玲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.35,0:12:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请指教
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说…说回来  公子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不来我家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.55,0:12:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是  那个  我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.73,0:12:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做我的丈…丈…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  为什么这么简单的事情说不出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是漂流到岛上的孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.53,0:12:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子…我可不想被小孩子说…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.39,0:12:41.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真失礼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把淑女说成小孩是侮辱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃深受打击了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:51.11,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  不要  不要  不要～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:53.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样  作为赔礼  今天和雪乃约会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:55.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.24,0:12:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  那边的公子是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:13:00.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这早熟的小鬼  还早十年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子是雪乃的东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.11,0:13:06.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.48,0:13:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊  熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不逃的话  就要死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要尽快离开这个岛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:19.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.43,0:13:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你准备的很丰盛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞒着铃出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.18,0:13:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说被绑架出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.83,0:13:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这里是哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎感觉到了杀气…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:38.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉你在为难什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明还是白天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.48,0:13:45.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我叫千影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…感觉很懂礼貌  这是个正常的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…我是行人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.99,0:13:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千影小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.18,0:14:01.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是一样的手段？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲过了我的吹箭…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.56,0:14:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是不同的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.83,0:14:12.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  连射式？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么有趣的研究对象  可不能让你逃跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.35,0:14:26.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊  上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:30.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.76,0:14:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.66,0:14:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.41,0:14:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.66,0:14:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么大家都要追着我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.52,0:14:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:54.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人是婆婆叫我照看的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.15,0:14:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽是这样说  你却是想自己独占男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:14:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也想和铃一样跟他约会  亲热什么的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:05.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那种事情没做过的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.16,0:15:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲热又是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.47,0:15:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底  大家这么围着人家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:10.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这岛到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:11.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.27,0:15:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这岛上没有男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.65,0:15:19.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除你以外
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就…就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.24,0:15:24.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这全是女人的岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我一个男的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女婿殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:30.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.91,0:15:32.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开  开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:37.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.26,0:15:39.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有几条命都不够的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.08,0:15:49.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然铃照顾了我许多  但我还是决定要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随他去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.25,0:15:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:57.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.63,0:16:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.04,0:16:05.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追我追的那么厉害的人  还真这么容易就放我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.64,0:16:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝兰岛吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.12,0:16:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然受了不少苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.83,0:16:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样看还真是美丽的岛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:16.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗  让他走…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:19.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他自身体验是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.82,0:16:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.88,0:16:25.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这岛的周围都被漩涡所包围
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:30.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到不了外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.64,0:16:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想从我的手里逃出去是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:37.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  行人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…头冒星星  好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:42.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:46.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅靠自己要出这岛是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.34,0:16:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:50.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎么努力绝对不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.17,0:16:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不行的  放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.58,0:16:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去做过怎么会知道！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.57,0:17:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么想做的话  先把我打倒了再去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然做不到的话  就别说大话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:14.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的「绝对不行」已经罗嗦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.85,0:17:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  我会死心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.98,0:17:23.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎么试都没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你超越不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.95,0:17:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  行人  要做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再试一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.88,0:17:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你来说是绝对不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.05,0:17:45.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了绝对不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.79,0:17:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.69,0:17:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没结束！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.99,0:17:59.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:01.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.58,0:18:02.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不要做了比较好…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.16,0:18:10.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我完全没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.32,0:18:13.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样乱来下去  不单单只是受重伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.23,0:18:18.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就只看出我到现在都被打飞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我有好好的用身体记住漩涡的模式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.07,0:18:28.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么失败  人所做的事情没有一样是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.07,0:18:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是爷爷的名言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.35,0:18:33.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经看穿这一切了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.47,0:18:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的已经完全改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:40.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢做无意义的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.67,0:18:41.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认真倔强的男人真是不讨厌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.03,0:18:45.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明连什么是男人都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.28,0:18:46.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.29,0:18:49.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:51.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会成功吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.79,0:18:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  那边不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  如我所想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漩涡和漩涡之间有间隙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.43,0:19:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈～  看到了吗  这回是我的胜利…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:16.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎…虎鲸？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.31,0:19:19.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  这家伙是来妨碍我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  一个又一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:24.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.79,0:19:27.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做什么的时候总会有碍事的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:30.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经忍不住了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.86,0:19:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要这样受别人做主的人生！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.64,0:19:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…击中了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:40.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:43.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不想打到你～的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好运  现在的话能通过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:46.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.07,0:19:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:19:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了  已经没有力气了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:20:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太乱来…了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.06,0:20:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果…我还是什么都没做成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:08.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这深海里  成为虎鲸的饲料吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.35,0:20:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来救我的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.48,0:20:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:22.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.01,0:20:35.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生鱼片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:36.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.91,0:20:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生鱼片是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.49,0:20:48.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:54.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那些漩涡外面的地方  有最大的激流漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且任何东西都会被卷裂  吸入海底
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.97,0:21:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生鱼片是为了不让任何人接近而巡视着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.81,0:21:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.86,0:21:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说不能离开这个岛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.71,0:21:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是行人很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.21,0:21:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎也被感动了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.51,0:21:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.62,0:21:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像到现在为止都没有像这样全力贯彻自己的想法到底的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.42,0:21:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉轻松了许多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.00,0:21:32.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到蓝兰岛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.92,0:21:39.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透明了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.62,0:21:46.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.92,0:21:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.46,0:23:14.17,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「被围追的  女婿殿下」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.12,0:23:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.53,0:23:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样这个岛也得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.07,0:23:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  行人  振作一点
